00:07:14.220 --> 00:07:19.710
And basically, every second of every day,
four people download QuickTime.

00:07:19.740 --> 00:07:22.650
We've got incredible distribution
of this architecture,

00:07:22.650 --> 00:07:25.260
and the infrastructure to
deliver this across all the

00:07:25.260 --> 00:07:28.340
different languages we support,
and across all the different

00:07:28.340 --> 00:07:30.300
ways that it can be distributed.

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.290
From our website.

00:07:31.320 --> 00:07:34.750
And this alone puts us very much,
you know, at the top of the heap with

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:36.160
respect to distribution.

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:39.760
But this is just one way in which
QuickTime is actually distributed.

00:07:39.780 --> 00:07:44.850
It's referred to on upwards of about
20,000 websites every day refer

00:07:44.850 --> 00:07:47.230
people to our site to get QuickTime.

