directories for using the Apache web

00:54:52.580 --> 00:54:55.700
server and Mac OS X server,
and then it's going to pop up

00:54:55.700 --> 00:54:57.400
a preview for me in Safari.

00:54:57.400 --> 00:55:00.070
So click create page.

00:55:00.070 --> 00:55:02.580
It's off doing its thing
with the web server,

00:55:02.580 --> 00:55:07.470
