But before you do,
something terrible has to happen.

01:03:12.870 --> 01:03:13.620
So I think you get the idea.

01:03:13.730 --> 01:03:14.920
It's very, very high quality.

01:03:14.920 --> 01:03:17.280
In addition,
you can do things that you could

01:03:17.280 --> 01:03:18.590
never do with the HD content.

